{"tid":1716857,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"用一個理性D嘅角度 睇點解要反抗","createTime":"2019-11-13T12:44:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T12:44:42.000Z","uid":320768,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4114351d0030c800ddfff35052cadb4f49ff437d","tid":1716857,"uid":320768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:44:43.000Z","msg":"每一個人<br />\n都係生而平等自由<br />\n喺戰爭狀態下 <br />\n人與人之間 會為左自己嘅利益會傷害對方<br />\n<br />\n每一個公民 <br />\n都希望喺唔受到人地侵犯之下 保障自己<br />\n因為咁樣 我地選擇犧牲自己一部分嘅主權<br />\n將管治權賦予政府 <br />\n而政府從此背起咗保䕶市民嘅責任<br />\n呢個係公民同政府之間嘅契約<br />\n<br />\n但衣家 政府好似擁有絕對主權錦<br />\n唔單止無視民意 <br />\n仲將黑警濫暴 視為理所當然<br />\n政府 已經單方面違咗約<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好想話比藍絲港豬聽<br />\n我哋 唔喺暴徒 <br />\n而係喺喥做一個基本公民應該做嘅事<br />\n<br />\n我地有權賦予權力比政府<br />\n有權選擇我地想點<br />\n亦有權收取我地比政府嘅權利<br />\n<br />\n我哋唔係喺度爭取<br />\n只係喺度攞番屬於自己嘅野<br />\n因為你衣家比被人剝奪緊嘅 係你原有嘅自由 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>所以更加要堅持 <br />\n所以更加要撐落去<br />\n各位手足 死都唔割<br />\n漫漫長路 有你有我</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 加油<br />\n香港人 反抗<br />\n香港人 報仇</span></span>"}]}